description: Iconic Court Square Press expansive 1 BR loft conveniently located across from the Broadway "T" in the heart of vibrant South Boston. Retaining many details from its industrial printing press origins - expansive timber ceilings, exposed brick, oversized windows – cleverly combined with modern sophisticated flair – granite/stainless kitchen, gas cooking, hardwood floors, subway-tiled bath. Flexible west-facing layout allows for dedicated living, dining, office, exercise spaces with a generous walk-in closet. Luxury full-service building offers 24/7 concierge, in-ground roof-top pool terrace with grills and skyline views, screening room, beautiful zen courtyard, on-site fitness facility, even a dog run for your beloved pooch. In-unit laundry, central A/C, bike storage and on-site maintenance staff. With excellent proximity to award winning shops and restaurants, easy commuting via transit or highway and one of Boston’s hottest locations, don't wait! Elevate your urban lifestyle now!
